==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: industrialize
<hw>industrialize</hw> <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To make industrial; to
develop so that most of the working population is engaged in
non-agricultural labor; to develop economically; -- of nations or
geographical areas; <as>as, to <ex>industrialize</ex> underdeveloped
nations</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>industrialized</ent>⟦br⟧
